            <entry valign="top"><para>Description</para></entry>
          </row>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para> <guilabel moreinfo="none">Abbreviated
            Name</guilabel> </para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Abbreviated name of the counterparty,
            uniquely identifying it within your company. This is used as a
            reference key of the record and is generally not displayed in
            transactions.</para></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para> <guilabel
            moreinfo="none">Name</guilabel> </para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Name of the counterparty (most often a
            company name) as it appears when used in a transaction
            record.</para></entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable>

